lead_paragraph: Former All Blacks winger Cory Jane has signed a two-year contract with Japan's Toshiba Brave Lupus, though he will return to play for the Wellington Hurricanes next year, his Super Rugby franchise said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Former All Blacks Winger Jane Heads to Japan
